      "title": "Interim budget speech on Aug 30",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The interim budget speech or the Appropriation (Amendment) Bill will be delivered to the parliament on the 30th of August, by President Ranil Wickremesinghe in his capacity as the Minister of Finance.",
        "Meanwhile, the debate on the budget has been scheduled for August 31 and September 01."
      ],
